com.joliciel.talismane.posTagger

Interface PosTagSequence

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ClassificationSolution, Comparable<PosTagSequence>, Iterable<PosTaggedToken>, Solution

    public interface PosTagSequence
extends Iterable<PosTaggedToken>, Comparable<PosTagSequence>, ClassificationSolution
    A sequence of postags applied to a given token sequence.
    Author:
    Assaf Urieli
